results.description: Very well cared for home ready for a new owner.  This great home features new baseboards and wood laminate/tile flooring throughout.  Remodeled stone fireplace with a wood burning insert to keep you warm during the winter and ceiling fans throughout to help keep you cool during the summer.  Solar panels to help keep the power bill low when it matters the most.  Remodeled Kitchen and bathrooms!  Newer septic tank!  RV/Boat parking potential. Additional pictures and a 3D Tour coming soon.  Call with any questions before it hits the market.

Well Maintained Desirable Hi Ranch with New Solar Panel System, Boiler/Water Tank, New Roof. and Vinyl Fence. Impressive Hard Wood Floors in Bedrooms, Den, Living Room / Dining Area. Ground Level includes Laundry Room, Bedroom/Office With Ose PLUS Legal One Bedroom Apartment with Off-Street Parking. Spacious Deck via Kitchen with Direct Access to Large Backyard with Room for Entertaining. Storage Shed is a Gift.

You will find a lot of open space from the front door through to the kitchen loads of natural light too, hardwood except in kitchen, nice size kitchen to eat in, or in the dining/breakfast area garage has extra storage area to the left

Newly rebuilt inside, this home has all new flooring, walls, doors, windows, cabinets, counter tops, bathrooms, lighting, When you open the door you are greated with vaulted ceilings and a wide open floor plan. Dual sided fireplace off the kitchen leads to a additional bonus room in the back. The backyard is large enough to accomodate a pool and the side yard is wide enough to accomodate RV parking.
wow just in time for the new year! 3 bedroom 1 bath wood floors on  quiet street waiting just for you. Great value, level yard, hardwood floors and more. don't miss this opportunity
Beautiful single family home that contains 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Walking distance from parks ans schools.

Updated single story 3 bedroom, 2 bath in the heart of Gilbert! Home is located on a great lot. Backyard is gorgeous with a custom built oversized covered patio and private covered hot tub area. This home does not disappoint!

Coming Soon! This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, horse property, located on over 1 1/2 acres in Surprise will be coming on the market soon! Don’t miss your opportunity to own this home and call it yours!

Beautiful Clearwater Beach condo is looking for a new owner.  This SPLIT 2 bedroom 2 bath unit with 2 large balconies has amazing views from the Master and Living room balconies.  You get the best of both worlds.  Not only do you have amazing views of the Intercoastal Bay, but you also are located right on the Gulf of Mexico and close to everything!  The Regatta Beach Club features one of the greatest beachfront condo living styles with fitness gym and cafe style computer rooms with great gulf views, private indoor large screen theatre with seating for 13 persons, large heated pool, shuffle board, boardwalk, pool and card rooms and staffed Hotel Like Lobby. Enjoy scenic sunrises and sentimental sunsets.

This 3/2 house is ready for a new buyer. A newly painted exterior and a new front door are the first of many upgrades that will welcome you into this home. Granite counter tops in the master bathroom with a glass enclosed walk-in shower. The eat-in kitchen has granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances. It even comes with a wall mounted TV. With a split floor plan, a two car garage and plenty of upgrades like the new laminated floors in the den and custom blinds. This home is move-in ready.

COMING SOON!  

Cozy Modernist Cottage in a marvelous historic neighborhood... This designer home has it all: Updated Baths, beautiful modern kitchen, luxury details and surfaces. Sublime interior to die for! Charming yard and great neighborhood for the romantic in us all. Near Encanto Park & Golf Course with tennis and basketball courts, pool, bicycle paths and picnic areas. Close to downtown sporting events, museums, theater and great restaurants. Located minutes from Phoenix College and St Joseph's Hospital.

This custom built, 5 bed, 5 full bath home is one of a kind & includes a separate, stand alone 850sf 1 bed, 1 full bath MIL suite (or Air BnB rental) complete with HC accessibility and granite kitchen counters. Built with SIP's panels and completely sealed, double pane argon filled windows and foam roof insulation gives exceptional R value. Rock climbing wall, 450sf outbuilding workshop, sunken trampoline, sport court, 40' RV parking with full hook up/sewer dump and home video monitoring system are just a few things this home offers. The full basement includes a bedroom, full bath and large storage area for long term pantry storage. The 10' diving pool was just completely redone with mini pebbletec. It has nearly a 1/2 acre of plants and grass which provide a beautiful yard to relax and play. This beautiful, energy efficient, kids paradise will not last! Appraised at $769k in 2017.
